  <summary date="2022-09-20T17:41:19Z" status="Introduced in House">Jobs and Opportunities for Medicaid Act

This bill establishes work requirements under Medicaid for able-bodied adults (i.e., those between the ages of 18 and 65 and who are not otherwise unable to work due to a medical condition, family situation, or other listed reason).</summary>
